<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>SpillStudies - FAQ</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.css" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 20px;
        background-color: #faf6f2;
      }
      
      .faq-container {
        margin: 40px 0;
      }
      
      .faq-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }
      
      .faq-header h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        color: #5d4037;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      
      .faq-header p {
        color: #8d6e63;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }
      
      .faq-item {
        background: #efebe9;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        border-left: 4px solid #d7ccc8;
      }
      
      .faq-question {
        padding: 20px;
        background: #8d6e63;
        color: white;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
      }
      
      .faq-question:hover {
        background: #6d4c41;
      }
      
      .faq-answer {
        padding: 20px;
        display: none;
        background: white;
      }
      
      .faq-answer p {
        margin: 0;
      }
      
      .faq-item.active .faq-answer {
        display: block;
      }
      
      .faq-item.active .faq-question {
        background: #6d4c41;
      }
      
      .faq-toggle {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include("../partials/header") %>
    
    <div class="faq-container">
      <div class="faq-header">
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <p>Find answers to common questions about SpillStudies online learning platform</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span>How do I sign up for courses on SpillStudies?</span>
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Browse our course catalog, and click "Learn more" on any course. For detailed course information and you can enroll from there.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span>Can I access courses on mobile devices?</span>
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes! SpillStudies is fully responsive and works on all devices. Check individual course pages (using "Learn More") to see any specific mobile requirements.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span>Are certificates provided upon course completion?</span>
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Most courses offer certificates. You can find certification details on each course's page by clicking "Learn More" in our course catalog.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span>How do I contact instructors if I have questions?</span>
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Using the instructors page, you can get information on any of the instructors and then you may join their live sessions or use the contact form in Contact page.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span>What payment methods do you accept?</span>
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>We accept major credit cards and PayPal.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span>Can I get a refund if I'm not satisfied with a course?</span>
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee. Refund policies for specific courses may vary.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <script>
      document.querySelectorAll('.faq-question').forEach(question => {
        question.addEventListener('click', () => {
          const item = question.parentNode;
          item.classList.toggle('active');
          
          const toggle = question.querySelector('.faq-toggle');
          if (item.classList.contains('active')) {
            toggle.textContent = '-';
          } else {
            toggle.textContent = '+';
          }
        });
      });
    </script>
  </body>
  <%- include("../partials/footer") %>
</html>